==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Motorbike
<hw>Mo"tor*bike`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>a light
two-wheeled vehicle containing a motor for propulsion. It is lighter in
construction and has a lower speed than a <er>motorcycle</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <specif>Specifically:</specif> <def>a small motorcycle
with a low frame and small weels and elevated handlebars.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> minibike.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <specif>Specifically:</specif> <def>a bicyle with a motor
attached for propulsion.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>motorcoach</ent>⟦br⟧
